title: Kendall Jenner Tweets Message to Lamar Odom Amid His Hospitalization
text: Kendall Jenner has taken to her Twitter account to send Lamar Odom a message. The 19-year-old supermodel tweeted to Khloe Kardashian‘s ex, “please don’t go.” Lamar, 35, was found unconscious in a Las Vegas brothel on Tuesday (October 13) and was rushed to a hospital, where his condition is largely unknown but sources say he [...] »
